    {
      "para_id": "Q001642.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Gilgameš of Enegir , his master , Ur-Namma , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , when he built the temple of Nanna , dedicated this ( vase ) for his well-being . Whoever erases its inscription , may Gilgameš curse him !"
    }
  ],
